videos.headline: App State LB slaps opponent in the face
videos.description: Jourdan Heilig is called for unsportsmanlike conduct after getting in his opponent's face. He's reprimanded on the sidelines by the head coach and his fellow teammates.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (App State LB slaps opponent in the face) 2019/12/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Pittman lays out for UAB touchdown
videos.description: Tyler Johnston III puts the ball in the air to Hayden Pittman for a 25-yard touchdown vs. No. 20 Appalachian State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pittman lays out for UAB touchdown) 201912/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: UAB's Watkins breaks a tackle, rushes in for 2nd TD
videos.description: Austin Watkins takes the pass from Tyler Johnston III, breaks a tackle and takes off for the second touchdown in the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UAB's Watkins breaks a tackle, rushes in for 2nd TD) 2019/12/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hennigan hauls in catch from corner of the end zone
videos.description: App State's Thomas Hennigan jumps up to make a touchdown catch from Zac Thomas in the second half of action vs. UAB.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hennigan hauls in catch from corner of the end zone) 2019/12/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Evans' unconventional scoop-and-score TD for App State
videos.description: Darrynton Evans picks up the loose ball outside the pile and takes it to the end zone for an App State score in the second half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Evans' unconventional scoop-and-score TD for App State) 2019/12/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: App State scores second scoop-and-score of game
videos.description: Nick Hampton sacks UAB quarterback Tyler Johnston III forcing him to fumble. App State's Trey Cobb comes up with the loose ball and takes it 24 yards to the house.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (App State scores second scoop-and-score of game) 2019/12/21 ESHEET
